https://java.net/jira/browse/JERSEY-2888
https://bugs.eclipse.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=463169
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/33722764/glassfish-error-when-producing-json

Bug in GlassFish 4.1.1 when use JAX-RS Jersey implementation and EclipseLink MOXY JSON provider.

SOLUTION: place patched file org.eclipse.persistence.moxy.jar to folder %GLASSFISH_PATH%/glassfish/modules